5
One Move Captures Black (14)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to Play.\b0
\par Black has a lot of eyespace and appears to have no weaknesses.
\par
\par However, there is a fatal defect in this shape. Black's group is in danger of having a shortage of liberties. If you take this into consideration, you can capture black easily.
\par }
