Diagram 1 (Failure)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}{\f1\fmodern\fprq2\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par First, a failure.
\par If you could capture black by crawling at 1, it would not really be a problem at all.
\par
\par \pard\nowidctlpar\qj Black lives with 2. Instead of 2, black could also live with \b\f1 A\b0\f0 .
\par }
