Diagram 3 (Vital Point, But)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 is the vital point. However, white must think carefully when black plays 2.
\par
\par If white hastily plays at 3, black can resist at 4 making a pae.
\par
\par White should capture black unconditionally.
\par }
